An outpouring of condolences has dominated social media ever since news of veteran musician Dan Tshanda's death was confirmed on Saturday evening. Family spokespersonÂ Moudy Ngwedzeni Mudzielwana confirmed the news through a media statement on Facebook. "Dalom Music is hereby confirming the passing away of music maestro Dan Tshanda today. He suffered a heart failure earlier and Sandton Mediclinic where he was declared dead," read the statement. Memorial and funeral details are yet to be announced by the family. High-profile celebrities including Yvonne Chaka Chaka and fans from across the continent have since paid touching tribute to the star.